{"tid":1135611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倘窺淫罪立法 觀察他人也能定罪","createTime":"2019-05-02T11:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T13:55:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f75850bfe6c264e10f3d41851773e2cd692574a","tid":1135611,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"報告書建議，應訂立一項特定的窺淫罪，內容參照英格蘭《2003年性罪行法令》第67條，將未經同意下為性的目的，對另一人進行觀察或視像記錄的行為刑事化，這類行為嚴重侵犯另一人的性自主權。<br />\n<br />\n此外，法改會建議訂立一項特定的未經同意下拍攝裙底罪，內容參照英格蘭《2003年性罪行法令》新加入的第67A條，同時需顧及以下事項：<br />\n‧ 未經同意下拍攝裙底行為不論目的為何，皆應定為不合法。這項「全面性」條文有一個好處，可將受僱於第三者的人所作出的未經同意下拍攝裙底行為刑事化。"},{"pid":"357c1c6930dc2220844a822ec8c43022f685db2f","tid":1135611,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"舉證全憑被望者"},{"pid":"e1245b604db93f30778c9bb9ca2eda65e5141873","tid":1135611,"uid":199590,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"你唔望我點知我望你"},{"pid":"3f7f9a99c324f07b61c663ae3ec6d9b2e4688ca2","tid":1135611,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"未經同意下拍攝裙底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人就可以脾人影褲底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fff1e5189734c4a63865fae4868c010722647b5","tid":1135611,"uid":1971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RjK5s6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RjK5s6.png&h=44766d6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed378040e6647c0dc416ef70bfe32af07e59bd38","tid":1135611,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"拉曬啲賤種偷拍狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7d8b78ec1bf97745a9349c9b8cd1073a141701","tid":1135611,"uid":55597,